Program: Outlook
Title: 18/04/2011
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00fz841
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 19 Apr 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world: today, a woman who escaped from the Libyan city of Misrata, the street kids making radio programmes in Delhi, and the first woman to sail non stop around the world - not just once, but three times!